757
00:34:23,866 --> 00:34:29,806
So this is sort of the host
side of setting resources


758
00:34:29,806 --> 00:34:31,226
that are going to be
used in your Shader.


759
00:34:31,936 --> 00:34:34,606
And there's a corresponding
Shader side


