00:36:00,066 --> 00:36:02,176
which is the buffer
that we just bound.


791
00:36:02,756 --> 00:36:05,346
And the second parameter is
this thing that's attributed


792
00:36:05,346 --> 00:36:08,456
with the vertex ID attribute,
