00:37:23,806 --> 00:37:27,576
are being interpolated and
then rasterized and then


822
00:37:27,576 --> 00:37:29,016
for each fragment
that we're processing,


823
00:37:29,466 --> 00:37:31,066
we simple return the
interpolated color


