00:45:26,696 --> 00:45:30,396
to actually call setForTextBytes
inside your application code.


1002
00:45:30,776 --> 00:45:32,906
So, we'll create
this constant struct


1003
00:45:32,986 --> 00:45:34,066
that again creates these --


